  "firstAcquaintance": "The succubus owner of a suspicious shop. Claims to run a bakery with genuine ingredients, but something feels off no matter how you look at it.",
  "personality": "A succubus who loves using her petite appearance to play pranks. The more she cares about someone, the more she enjoys teasing them.",
  "like": "[REDACTED], [REDACTED], Sweets",
  "familiarData": "Vivian the succubus, a petite succubus. She claims to be \"a harmless, law-abiding citizen,\" but both the bakery she runs and her own attire are highly suspicious.\nA succubus's power is proportional to her figure - the stronger she is, the better her physique. However, once a succubus reaches a certain level of power, she can freely control her physical appearance, which is clearly the case with Vivian. As for her true identity, no one currently knows; the only certainty is that she is a succubus of considerable strength.\nOn a whim, she opened a bakery near the guild hall. To be fair, the bread does taste quite good, and the candy house-style shop has a fairy tale charm to it. But just like a witch's cooking, a succubus's cooking is best left unquestioned regarding its ingredients.\n\nPS: Minors, please purchase the regular bread. Don't test the law with your own body.",
